---
import Layout from '../../Base.astro';
import SimpleHero from '../../components/SimpleHero.astro';
import FeaturedArticles from '../../components/FeaturedArticles.astro';
import ServicesRelatedWork from '../../components/ServicesRelatedWork.astro';
import '../../styles/pages/_services-list.scss';
---

<Layout
  title="Ecommerce Development | Florida Digital Agency"
  description="We design and build ecommerce systems that reduce friction, improve conversions, and support long-term growth across Shopify and WooCommerce."
>
  <SimpleHero
    tagline="Ecommerce Development"
    title="Ecommerce That Actually Converts"
    description="Selling online isn’t just about having a store—it’s about removing friction from every step of the buying process. We build ecommerce systems that are fast, intuitive, and designed to turn traffic into revenue."
    lottieFile="ecommerce.json"
  />

  <div class="wrapper wrapper--narrow" style="padding-bottom: 100px; text-align: center;">
    We are certified partners with both
    <a href="https://woocommerce.com/development-services/kelp-creative-agency/232621912/">WooCommerce</a>
    and Shopify.
  </div>

  <div class="service-body">
    <div class="wrapper wrapper--narrow">
      <h2>Where most ecommerce sites fall short</h2>
      <p>
        Most ecommerce sites don’t fail because of their products—they fail because of friction. Slow load times,
        confusing navigation, broken checkout flows, and disconnected systems all contribute to lost revenue.
      </p>
      <p>
        A customer who is ready to buy should never have to think about how your site works. When the experience is
        unclear or inefficient, they leave.
      </p>

      <h2>What we focus on</h2>
      <p>
        We treat ecommerce as a system, not just a storefront. Every part of the experience—from product discovery to
        checkout—should work together to support a single goal: conversion.
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>Clear product structure and navigation</li>
        <li>Fast, performance-focused builds</li>
        <li>Optimized cart and checkout experiences</li>
        <li>Seamless integrations with payment, shipping, and inventory systems</li>
        <li>Scalable platforms that grow with your business</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How we approach it</h2>
      <p>We start by understanding how your business sells—then build the system to support it.</p>

      <ol>
        <li>
          <strong>Define the buying journey:</strong> Identify how customers discover, evaluate, and purchase your products.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Structure the store:</strong> Organize products, categories, and content to reduce friction and improve
          clarity.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Design for conversion:</strong> Create layouts and interactions that guide users toward purchase.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Build and integrate:</strong> Develop the store and connect it to the tools that power your operations.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Refine and optimize:</strong> Continuously improve performance, usability, and conversion rates over time.
        </li>
      </ol>

      <h2>The outcome</h2>
      <p>
        A well-built ecommerce system removes friction, increases conversion rates, and gives your business a foundation
        that can scale without constant rework.
      </p>

      <p>
        <a href="/contact/" class="button button--green">Start a Project</a>
      </p>
    </div>

    <ServicesRelatedWork tag={84} />
  </div>

  <FeaturedArticles />
</Layout>
